###  https://sakuna.ph/SevereWinterConditions
:SevereWinterConditions rdf:type owl:Class ;
                        rdfs:subClassOf :ExtremeTemperature ;
                        rdfs:label "Severe Winter Conditions"@en ;
                        skos:definition "Severe winter conditions: Damage caused by snow and ice. Winter damage refers to damage to buildings, infrastructure, traffic (esp. navigation) inflicted by snow and ice in the form of snow pressure, freezing rain, frozen waterways etc." .


