###  https://sakuna.ph/WaveAction
:WaveAction rdf:type owl:Class ;
            rdfs:subClassOf :Hydrological ;
            rdfs:label "Wave Action"@en ;
            skos:definition "Wind-generated surface big waves that can occur near coastal areas or on the surface of any open body of water such as oceans, rivers, or lakes. The size of the wave depends on the strength of the wind and the distance traveled (fetch)." .


